dc_title_s: Eastern Turkey in Asia. Kars, sheet 7. Series I.D.W.O. no. 1522
dc_description_s: Great Britain. War Office. Intelligence Division. I.D.W.O. no. 1522. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 1522. Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. Some sheets from this set were revised and issued by War Office. Geographical Section. General Staff, published as G.S.G.S. no. 1522, 1522a. Series covers Mesopotamia and eastern Anatolian parts of Ottoman Empire. "Compiled at the Intelligence Division, War Office by Majro F.R. Maunsell, R.A. from Russian 5 Verst Maps, Editions 1898 (up to frontier) & Russian 1 Verst Maps, Editions 1898, 1901." With a glossary. Set is complete, see index.
